features: 𝗕𝗜𝗕𝗦 𝗣𝗔𝗖𝗜𝗙𝗜𝗘𝗥𝗦: A favorite for both moms and babies for over forty years! BIBS baby pacifiers allow your child to self-soothe by exercising their instinctive sucking instinct in the most natural way possible. Now in 4 unique styles, Colour, Supreme, Couture and De Lux. Check out the new BIBS Bities Teethers, BIBS Loops and BIBS Cuddle Cloth and Cuddle Swaddle

𝗦𝗘𝗧 𝗢𝗙 𝟮 𝗣𝗔𝗖𝗜𝗙𝗜𝗘𝗥𝗦: Each order includes 2 BIBS Supreme baby pacifiers which is available in 2 sizes (0 to 6 Months & 6 to 18 Months). As always, BIBS products are offered in a variety of beautiful colors and tones which are distinctively BIBS. Still undecided? Check out our new Try-it Collection which includes each of our popular pacifier styles. Makes the perfect gift for baby girls and baby boys

𝗦𝗨𝗣𝗥𝗘𝗠𝗘 𝗖𝗢𝗟𝗟𝗘𝗖𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡: New style, same BIBS quality. The elegant shield is designed to ensure optimal passage of air so that the skin around the mouth remains dry. The flat nipple is designed to support proper jaw development and minimize the pressure on the teeth. The nipple is symmetrically shaped and made of silicone.

𝗖𝗔𝗥𝗘 𝗜𝗡𝗦𝗧𝗥𝗨𝗖𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡𝗦: Sterilize each pacifier before use by pouring boiling water over it, squeezing any remaining water out, and letting dry for 4–6 hours. We recommend a replacement every 4-6 weeks for both safety and hygienic reasons. Rubber latex is a natural material and is affected by sunlight, high temperatures, and moisture. If you experience a change in the material, the pacifier must be replaced.

𝗠𝗔𝗗𝗘 𝗜𝗡 𝗗𝗘𝗡𝗠𝗔𝗥𝗞: Designed and manufactured in Denmark. BIBS pacifiers are made of the highest quality materials and are 100% free of BPA, PVC and phthalates. Always striving for excellence, BIBS pacifiers are often imitated but never duplicated.

productInformation.name: Care instructions
productInformation.value: ‎Care Instructions: Sterilize each pacifier before use by pouring boiling water over it, squeezing any remaining water out, and letting dry for 4–6 hours. For best hygiene practice, pacifiers should only be used for 4-6 weeks. Do not use a pacifier that shows changes in color or irregularities, though the nipple size may naturally expand with use.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Our Story BIBS is a premium Danish baby brand. Since the 1970's, we've been refining and improving our baby pacifiers. Our products are made using only the highest quality materials. Always striving for excellence, we produce baby pacifiers that are safe, functional and aesthetically pleasing. We're proud to offer our complete collection of premium baby pacifiers which include: BIBS Couture (our newest pacifier)BIBS Colour (our original pacifier)BIBS De LuxBIBS Supreme

BIBS Couture The BIBS Couture is our newest premium pacifier. It features an anatomically shaped nipple and will be the most sensitive for your child's jaw and gums. Available in 2 sizes (0-6 months & 6-18 months) and your choice of natural rubber or premium silicone. BIBs Colour Our iconic and original BIBS Colour baby pacifier. The cherry shaped nipple is made of natural rubber latex and resembles the shape and size of a mothers breast. BIBS Colour is available in 3 sizes (0-6 months, 6-18 months & 18-36 months) and many color combinations! BIBS De Lux The BIBS De Lux is a different take on the popular round design of the BIBS Colour. This premium pacifier features a bigger front and an extra handle. Available in 2 sizes (0-6 months & 6-18 months) and your choice of natural rubber or premium silicone. BIBS Supreme The BIBS Supreme pacifier has a new symmetrical nipple shape which reduces pressure to the teeth and jaw. The redesigned shield also allows more airflow for sensitive skin. Available in 2 sizes (0-6 months & 6-18 months) and your choice of natural rubber or premium silicone. BIBS Couture BIBS Colour BIBS De Lux BIBS Supreme

Quality, Design & Safety At BIBS, we strive for excellence. All of our premium baby pacifiers are made of the best possible materials and are 100% free from BPA's, PVC's and phthalates. We're proud to offer high qualify baby products which are both safe and aesthetically pleasing. There's a BIBS pacifier for every baby girl and baby boy! Each BIBS product is carefully designed and manufactured in Hilleroed, Denmark.

reviews.reviewText: The color labeled “vanilla” is actually pictured as the “ivory” color. I went by the color in the photo (ivory) so thought that’s what I was getting, but received vanilla, which is kind of a light tan.Good pacifiers, but disappointing that the color is so off.

reviews.reviewText: By far our favorite pacifiers!! Our baby loves the nipples on these by far the best of any other we’ve tried. But we love them too cause they look cute, they’re not too bulky, and we love all the different colors they have.
